{"tid":775572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「沙中綫報銷」梁國權：紅磡站安全測試決定大圍至紅磡站完工日期","createTime":"2018-08-11T09:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T07:12:32.000Z","uid":73915,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c833902d1ae018926b9fa3d63b274162eb975e8a","tid":775572,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"港鐵近期醜聞纏身，港鐵行政總裁梁國權今現身出席港鐵中期業績發布會，指沙中綫截至今年6月底，工程已完工86%，大圍至紅磡站所有新建車站的結構工程已大致完成，但目標完工日期視乎紅磡站月台層的核實及安全測試的進度及結果。該段原訂於2019年中通車，至於紅磡至會展站站的完工日期仍維持2021年。<br />\n梁國權又指，對沙中綫工程監管方面有不足，再次致歉，會盡一切努力配合調查委員會調查，董事局轄下的工程委員會亦檢討公司的項目管理程序，並會研究改善通報機制。"},{"pid":"041ba7bff6c36edea833c7ca2991a60a4ff3df9f","tid":775572,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"GDP GOGOGO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90c9cacdc0118f67db5de8ddc3f4db450c35817","tid":775572,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:39:04.000Z","msg":"大圍撚睇住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7eb2c32f6f7221852b142f315f3da67cc3d4f7","tid":775572,"uid":77473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:57:39.000Z","msg":"下年的DSEr要考慮埋交通先好揀大學<br />\n一陣讀左咁耐書<br />\n冧月台死左就唔抵啦<br />\n利申:in ust we trust"},{"pid":"3f8c10b541e0e1a05b84105befb50466957c7b63","tid":775572,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:58:49.000Z","msg":"MTR平時對住d細野就好撚惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e06132091b228d498fad815b0c377ca82ebdf78","tid":775572,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f8c10b541e0e1a05b84105befb50466957c7b63","tid":775572,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:58:49.000Z","msg":"MTR平時對住d細野就好撚惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass